headline: DDB Chicago Wins Creative and Strategy Assignment for Bimbo Global
summary: DDB Chicago has been appointed to lead the global creative and strategy assignment for the Bimbo masterbrand, part of Grupo Bimbo, the world's largest baking company, following a competitive pitch.
